---
// Testimonials.astro - Depoimentos de clientes
---

<section class="py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white dark:from-gray-950 dark:to-gray-900">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16 animate-fade-in-up">
      <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">
        Autoescolas que Confiam no <span class="gradient-text">Novus CFC</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Leia depoimentos de proprietários e gerentes de autoescolas que transformaram seus negócios com nosso software de agendamento online.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonials Grid -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:border-[#6f0a59] animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
        <!-- Stars -->
        <div class="flex gap-1 mb-4">
          <span class="text-2xl">⭐</span>
          <span class="text-2xl">⭐</span>
          <span class="text-2xl">⭐</span>
          <span class="text-2xl">⭐</span>
          <span class="text-2xl">⭐</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Testimonial Text -->
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6 italic">
          "O Novus CFC revolucionou nossa forma de atender. Cortamos pela metade o tempo de atendimento e eliminou 100% dos conflitos de horário. Alunos marcam anytime, e temos mais tempo para estratégia."
        </p>

        <!-- Author -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[#6f0a59] to-[#ffcd00] flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">
            JM
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">João Marcos</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Proprietário - CFC Centro SP</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:border-[#6f0a59] animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
        <!-- Stars -->
        <div class="flex gap-1 mb-4">
          <span class="text-2xl">⭐</span>
          <span class="text-2xl">⭐</span>
          <span class="text-2xl">⭐</span>
          <span class="text-2xl">⭐</span>
          <span class="text-2xl">⭐</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Testimonial Text -->
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6 italic">
          "Financeiro organizado, relatórios automáticos, controle preciso de saldo. Finalmente temos visibilidade total do negócio. Sistema fácil de usar e suporte responsivo."
        </p>

        <!-- Author -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[#ff6b35] to-[#ffcd00] flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">
            AS
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Andreia Silva</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Gerente - Auto Escola Zona Leste</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:border-[#6f0a59] animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
        <!-- Stars -->
        <div class="flex gap-1 mb-4">
          <span class="text-2xl">⭐</span>
          <span class="text-2xl">⭐</span>
          <span class="text-2xl">⭐</span>
          <span class="text-2xl">⭐</span>
          <span class="text-2xl">⭐</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Testimonial Text -->
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6 italic">
          "Alunos amam! Antes ligavam todo dia. Agora marcam sozinhos, a qualquer hora. Satisfação aumentou bastante. Sistema profissional que transmite credibilidade."
        </p>

        <!-- Author -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[#6f0a59] to-[#ff6b35] flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">
            CF
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Carlos Fernandes</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Proprietário - CFC Sul Brasil</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Social Proof Stats -->
    <div class="mt-20 grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 p-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#6f0a59]/10 to-[#ffcd00]/10 dark:from-[#6f0a59]/20 dark:to-[#ffcd00]/20 rounded-2xl border border-[#6f0a59]/20 animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#6f0a59] dark:text-[#ffcd00] mb-2">+10</div>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 font-semibold">Autoescolas Ativas</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#6f0a59] dark:text-[#ffcd00] mb-2">+1k</div>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 font-semibold">Alunos Agendados</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#6f0a59] dark:text-[#ffcd00] mb-2">+10k</div>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 font-semibold">Aulas Marcadas</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#6f0a59] dark:text-[#ffcd00] mb-2">4.9/5</div>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 font-semibold">Avaliação Média</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Final CTA -->
    <div class="mt-16 text-center animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;">
      <a href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=5517997437646&text=Olá! Gostaria de saber mais sobre o Novus CFC" 
         target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
         class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-10 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#6f0a59] to-[#4d003d] hover:shadow-xl text-white font-bold rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl text-[#6f0a59] dark:text-[#ffcd00]">chat_bubble</span>
        Comece Agora - Fale com a Gente!
      </a>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm mt-4">
        Resposta em minutos • Sem compromisso
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .gradient-text {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6f0a59 0%, #ff6b35 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  :global(.dark) .gradient-text {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fbbf24 0%, #ffcd00 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  @keyframes fade-in-up {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes fade-in {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  .animate-fade-in-up {
    animation: fade-in-up 0.8s ease-out forwards;
  }

  .animate-fade-in {
    animation: fade-in 0.8s ease-out forwards;
  }
</style>
